rode at the state fair.

00:35.220 --> 00:36.420
Please exit to the left.

00:36.610 --> 00:37.696
Man, that was lame.

00:37.720 --> 00:39.546
Why, if I built a roller
coaster, I would...

00:39.570 --> 00:41.746
- That's it!
- I know what we're gonna do today!

00:41.770 --> 00:44.126
- Phineas, Ferb!
- I'm gonna go pick up a few things.

00:44.150 --> 00:46.430
- You boys stays out of trouble, okay?
- Okay, Mom.

00:46.810 --> 00:49.050
We're gonna build a roller coaster!

00:50.590 --> 00:52.806
- I'm in charge, right?
- You did tell them I'm in charge.

00:52.830 --> 00:53.727
Relax, Candace.

00:53.751 --> 00:54.986
Nobody has to be in charge.

00:55.010 --> 00:56.426
But what if there's an emergency?

00:56.450 --> 00:57.276
Like what?

00:57.300 --> 00:58.300
What if, uh...

00:58.610 --> 01:02.600
What if a satellite falls out of
orbit and crashes into the house?

01:02.810 --> 01:05.190
- If that happens, you're in charge.
- Yes.

01:05.670 --> 01:07.530
Mom says I'm in charge,
conditionally.

01:07.690 --> 01:09.346
- Whatever.
- Wait a minute.

01:09.370 --> 01:11.340
