- Homework.

01:11.510 --> 01:12.626
It's summer.

01:12.650 --> 01:14.790
That's cool,
you wait till the last minute then.

01:15.360 --> 01:16.850
Well, I'm watching you.

01:18.140 --> 01:20.340
And I'm in charge...
conditionally!

01:23.510 --> 01:25.120
