01:28.590 --> 01:29.866
well, you know, conditionally.

01:29.890 --> 01:32.106
Oh, if you go, can you
see if Jeremy is there?

01:32.130 --> 01:34.746
No, no, he's the cute one that works at Mr.
Slushy Burger.

01:34.770 --> 01:37.136
Yeah, he totally smiled at me
the last time I was there.

01:37.160 --> 01:38.420
I just about died!

01:38.950 --> 01:40.076
No, I told you I can't,

01:40.100 --> 01:41.396
I'm watching my brother and step-brother.

01:41.420 --> 01:42.566
Yeah, and they never get into trouble,

01:42.590 --> 01:43.716
'cause Mom never catches them.

01:43.740 --> 01:44.976
